# Currency Field for USD
currency field is Deciaml with two decimal digit and maximum of 12 digits.

# Database Constraints:
Balance cannot be negative in a wallet,
And hence no need to check every time we can let insertions and updates be optimistic

# number of wallet per user
number of wallet per user is one made by OneToOne Field

# select for update
rows that are going to be updated are going to be locked while in transaction